%h1.text-center Listing categories
- if categories.empty?
  .alert.alert-info.alert-big.text-center 
    There no any categories yet.
    -if user_signed_in?
      But you can add some new ones.
- else
  .col-md-6.col-md-offset-3
    %table.table.table-striped.table-hover
      %tbody
        - categories.each do |category|
          %tr
            %td= category.name
            %td.text-right
              = link_to 'Show', category
              - if user_signed_in? && current_user.admin?
                &#47;
                = link_to 'Edit', edit_category_path(category)
                &#47;
                = link_to 'Destroy', category, method: :delete, data: { confirm: 'Are you sure?' }
    
- if user_signed_in? && current_user.admin?
  .col-md-6.col-md-offset-3
    %hr
    .text-center= link_to 'New Category', new_category_path, class: 'btn btn-primary'